Summary: Describes the TextureProgressBar class, a texture-based progress bar.

TextureProgressBar
Inherits: Range < Control < CanvasItem < Node < Object

Texture-based progress bar. Useful for loading screens and life or stamina bars.
---CHUNK---
Document: TextureProgressBar
Path: godot/classes/class_textureprogressbar.rst
Summary: Describes the TextureProgressBar node, which uses textures for progress display.

TextureProgressBar works like ProgressBar, but uses up to 3 textures instead of Godot's Theme resource. It can be used to create horizontal, vertical and radial progress bars.
---CHUNK---
