*   texture_over (Texture2D):
*   texture_progress (Texture2D):
*   texture_progress_offset (Vector2): Default: Vector2(0, 0)
*   texture_under (Texture2D):
*   tint_over (Color): Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1)
*   tint_progress (Color): Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1)
